{"type":"text","timestamp":1775887757483,"sessionID":"ses_284d83369ffeu6xf7SuTZDf0Mj","part":{"id":"prt_d7b28901e001L9ygilQPieOS31","messageID":"msg_d7b288780001qSWq4BBiuI5Sul","sessionID":"ses_284d83369ffeu6xf7SuTZDf0Mj","type":"text","text":"## AR-037 — PCAP 分析器示例应用 Archive\n\n### What Was Completed ✅\n\n**Core Implementation:**\n- `examples/pcap_analyzer.py` (388 lines) - Standalone PCAP analyzer with:\n  - Protocol detection (TCP/UDP/HTTP)\n  - IP/port statistics extraction\n  - HTTP method analysis\n  - DNS query extraction\n  - JSON/Text output formats\n  - CLI via Typer\n\n- `examples/pcap_analyzer_agent.py` - AgentCube SDK integration with:\n  - `CodeInterpreterClient` usage\n  - Remote sandbox execution\n  - File upload/download handling\n  - Scapy installation in sandbox\n\n- `examples/requirements.txt` - Dependencies:\n  - `scapy>=2.5.0`\n  - `typer>=0.9.0`\n  - `agentcube-sdk>=0.1.0`\n  - `matplotlib>=3.7.0` (optional)\n\n**Architecture:**\n- Modular design with error handling\n- Type annotations throughout\n- Custom exception classes\n\n---\n\n### What Was Deferred ⏸️\n\n**Documentation:**\n- ❌ No dedicated `README.md` for PCAP analyzer example\n- ❌ No usage examples or troubleshooting guide\n\n**Test Data:**\n- ❌ No `sample_pcap.py` script for generating test PCAPs\n- ❌ No `test_pcaps/` directory with sample files (`basic_http.pcap`, `dns_queries.pcap`)\n\n**Directory Structure:**\n- ❌ Proposed `sdk-python/examples/pcap_analyzer/` structure not created\n- ❌ Implementation placed in root `examples/` instead\n\n**Testing:**\n- ❌ No unit tests for PCAP analyzer\n- ❌ No integration tests with AgentCube SDK\n\n**Features:**\n- ❌ HTTP payload extraction (only method detection)\n- ❌ Visualization (matplotlib dependency unused)\n- ❌ Batch PCAP analysis support\n- ❌ PCAPng format support\n\n---\n\n**Archive Location:** `changes/AR-037/`  \n**Status:** Partially implemented (core functionality complete, supporting infrastructure deferred)","time":{"start":1775887757481,"end":1775887757481}}}
